## Notes for Image Generation:
- Use Midjourney v6+ or DALL-E 3 for best results
- Maintain consistent color grading across all images (warm amber/brown tones to match oolong tea)
- Featured image should be generated first to establish visual style
- Cultural images (tea mountains, tea house) can use more artistic license for atmosphere
- All food images should look authentic and appetizing, not overly stylized
- Oolong tea color should be amber/golden-brown, not green or black
- Fish should appear white-fleshed (sea bass, snapper, or cod)
- Sauce should have glossy, rich appearance without looking greasy
